data.description: New construction without the new construction wait.  This beautiful 2-year-old home has 4 large bedrooms to include an ensuite with 2 large walk in closets. Walk in shower with dual rain head shower system. There is an upstairs loft with three additional bedrooms at the top of the stairs. Check out the laundry room. The chef kitchen has a gas range, granite counter tops, and a large island. There is an office and dining room as well as an eat in kitchen. This home is right over the NC line from VA. What are you waiting on schedule your private showing today.
